Per obtenir els exon names del hg38: exportar exons hg19 de R (Conrad.hg19 data)

#data(Conrad.hg19)
#write.table(exons.hg19, "exons.hg19.txt",sep = "\t", row.names = FALSE, quote = FALSE)

Add chr to first column:
awk '{print "chr"$0}' exons.hg19.txt > exons.hg19.bed



